Lapeyrouse, TLM
</taxonomicName>
([without number]
<emphasis id="B92FEA80FF9AFFEDFC6FF80DA11BB913" bold="true" box="[1017,1031,2031,2052]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="221">).</emphasis>
Image by courtesy of the herbarium TLM, reproduced with permission.
</paragraph>
